{
  "texts": [
    "Texture, color, and form were used since they are well-known global feature descriptors.",
    "The authors used KNN, LR, DT, RF, SVM, and other algorithms for model training.",
    "The RF model outperformed many other ML algorithms in our analysis with an impressive 94% accuracy rate (Table 5).",
    "The authors (K and Rao, 2019) use KNN and probabilistic neural networks (PNN) to detect and categorize different diseases affecting tomato leaves.",
    "The dataset comprises 600 picture samples from healthy and diseased tomato leaves in the field."
  ]
